metadata.name: Ciudades #13
metadata.description:
Generative image from the combination of 3 layers: sky (mostly covered by buildings), buildings 1, buildings 2. Each layer has 6 variations which could also be mirrored. The combination of the three layers create different cityscapes, most of them overcrowded. The resulting images reflect the overwhelming development of cities, as they try to capture and understand the rhythm within the chaos. 

The images are composed from original pictures of New York and Sao Paulo.

metadata.name: Pine Dream #82
metadata.description:
Pine dream by Asaf Slook (2022)

This work is an attempt to create a simple pen-like generated drawing, in a way that confuses the observer to perceive it to be a real unique hand-drawn piece.

Rare features:
- Lonely tree
- Static stroke
- Sunny day palette
- Dotted land
- Partial land
 
The best results are from 1000x1000 and above.

This work was created using p5.js and love :)

metadata.name: ostinato #160
metadata.description:
“ostinato” by pixelwank 

“In music, an ostinato is a motif or phrase that persistently repeats in the same musical voice, frequently in the same pitch.”

Inspired by the musical term, the piece is constructed of many duplicate layers, creating a larger symphony.

Thanks for collecting <3
R.I.F.F.
Remember it's for fun!
Shoutout Circolors for the support & frenship <3

In live mode, click the image or press 's' or 'S' to save png

Made with p5js
© pixelwank 2022

metadata.name: Fireworks #87
metadata.description:
Every token can output in 12 different aspect ratios:
1x1, 3x1, 3x2, 2x3, 4x3, 3x4, 5x4, 4x5, 16x9, 9x16, 16x10, 10x16

With 3 framing options:
1. No frame
2. Rectangle frame
3. Arched window

And downloadable in 4 different resolutions:
1. 1000px
2. 2000px
3. 4000px
4. 8000px

Click on the image in live view to unlock all these possibilities.

Made with p5.js.
Primary split 5% with The Processing Foundation.

metadata.name: Backrooms Level 455 #2
metadata.description:
What kind of gallery is this...

50 photographs developed from a virtual film roll, taken in a maze-like liminal space.

metadata.name: Comunidade #11
metadata.description:
Generative image from the combination of 5 layers: 1/sky, 2-4 /buildings (favelas) and hills, 5 /different elements that interact with the cityscape. Each layer has a different number of variations which could also be mirrored. The 
images are composed from original pictures of Rio de Janeiro.

Just like in the Ciudades series, in the Comunidade series the combination of the layers creates overcrowded landscapes in which the rhythm dialogues with chaos.

metadata.name: Dystopic message #3
metadata.description:
In a world where we destroy everything and everyone in search of "evolution" we tend to become more and more dystopic, to rescue from the ruins and destruction of the past, only using technology and "innovation" and so I bring "Dystopic message" a message that brings together the new, modern and technological with the old.

"Dystopic message"
an artwork created by Eduxdux
September 2022
